s_N=\ln N +\gamma+O\left(\frac1N\right)
\sum_{n=1}^N(\frac1{3n-1}+\frac1{3n-2}-\frac2{3n})=\sum_{n=1}^N(\frac1{3n-1}+\frac1{3n-2}+\frac1{3n})-\sum_{n=1}^N\frac1n=s_{3N}-s_N.
\sum_{n=1}^N(\frac1{3n-1}+\frac1{3n-2}-\frac2{3n})=\ln(3N)-\ln N+O\left(\frac1N\right)=\ln3+O\left(\frac1N\right).
\lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{k=1}^{n} \left(\frac1{3k-2}+\frac1{3k-1}+\frac1{3k}-\frac1k\right)=\lim_{n\to\infty}\frac{1}{n}\sum_{k=1}^{2n}\frac1{1+\frac{k}{n}}=\int_0^2\frac{1}{1+x}=\ln3.
\sum_{k=1}^n \left(\frac1{3k-2}+\frac1{3k-1}+\frac1{3k}-\frac3{3k}\right) = H_{3n}-H_n \sim \ln{3n}-\ln n = \ln 3.
